name: プロデューサー
text:
ああ
移動の時とかにも、寝やすいかなと思ってな
trans:
Yeah. I felt like it might help you get some rest when
you're moving around.

name: 甜花
text:
これがあれば……
どこでも……お昼寝、し放題……！
trans:
If Tenka has this... then she can... nap as much as she
wants... wherever she wants......!

name: プロデューサー
text:
はは、おはよう甜花
よく眠れたみたいだな
trans: Haha, good morning Tenka. You slept quite a bit.

name: 甜花
text:
うん……
にへへ……起きたら、プロデューサーさんが、いた……
trans:
Yeah......
Nihehe...... You were her... when Tenka woke up......
